  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201511/945b5a1b42344241af8f40553562a813.png\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t在英语六级作文中，尤其是议论文中，经常会在开头引出自己的观点。说到这，不少童鞋一定会用&quot;someone thinks ... and others thinks...&quot;，而这种句子完全不会吸引监考老师的，下面小编带你看一些别样的引出不同观点的万能模板：</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">1、People's views on... vary from person to person. Some hold that... . However, others believe that.... 人们对&hellip;&hellip;的观点因人而异。有些人认为.....然而其他人却认为&hellip;&hellip;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">看这个长度就已然鹤立鸡群。其实，也是一个蛮简单也好记的模板。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">2、Attitudes towards (drugs) vary from person to person. 人们对待吸毒的态度因人而异。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">乍一看，跟上句的开头神似，其实就是省略掉了&quot;people's&quot;，不仅清爽而且好像高端了一些。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">3、People may have different opinions on... 人们对&hellip;&hellip;可能会有不同的见解。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">又是一个婉转的句子，展示其客观性。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t4、There are different opinions among people as to... 关于&hellip;&hellip;人们的观点大不相同。</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;different&quot;虽拉低了水准，但&quot;as to&quot;又拯救了回来。</p>\n<p>\n\t5、Different people hold different attitudes toward (failure). 对(失败)人们的态度各不相同。</p>\n<p>\n\t这句话貌似亮点不多，顶多一个&quot;hold&quot;，但也是安全牌，容易理解。</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<strong>相关文章：</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p754723/\" target=\"_blank\">六级阅读：碰到这四种细读题型怎么解？</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">精品课程推荐：</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"><a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/3742299?source=16556\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">大学英语四级【救命班</span>】</a>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"><a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/3742200?source=16556\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"line-